  <brief_title>Melatonin Agonist Effects of Tasimelteon Versus Placebo in Patients With Major Depressive Disorder</brief_title>
  <acronym>MAGELLAN</acronym>
  <official_title>MAGELLAN: A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Masked, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel Study to Investigate the Safety and Efficacy of 20 Mg Tasimelteon Versus Placebo in Adult Subjects With Major Depressive Disorder Followed by a 52-Week Open-Label Extension</official_title>
